// Listing Endpoints

### Get All Listings
GET http://localhost:3000/api/listings

### Get Active Listings
GET http://localhost:3000/api/listings/active

### Get Listing by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/listings/1

### Get Listing by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/listings/99999

### Get Listing by ID (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/listings/invalid

### Get Seller's Listings
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/listings

### Get Seller's Listings (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/listings

### Get Seller's Active Listings
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/listings/active

### Get Active Listing by Stove
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/1/listing

### Get Active Listing by Stove (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/99999/listing

### Create Listing
POST http://localhost:3000/api/listings
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sellerId": 1,
    "stoveId": 1,
    "price": 5000
}

### Create Listing (different price)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/listings
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sellerId": 1,
    "stoveId": 2,
    "price": 10000
}

### Create Listing (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/listings
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sellerId": 1
}

### Create Listing (invalid price)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/listings
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sellerId": 1,
    "stoveId": 1,
    "price": -100
}

### Create Listing (stove already listed)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/listings
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sellerId": 1,
    "stoveId": 1,
    "price": 3000
}

### Update Listing Price
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/listings/1/price
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": 6000
}

### Update Listing Price (invalid price)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/listings/1/price
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": -50
}

### Update Listing Price (not found)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/listings/99999/price
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": 5000
}

### Cancel Listing
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/listings/1/cancel

### Cancel Listing (not found)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/listings/99999/cancel

### Delete Listing
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/listings/1

### Delete Listing (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/listings/99999

### Count Active Listings by Seller
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/active-listings/count

### Count Active Listings by Seller (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/active-listings/count
